374
00:15:19,079 --> 00:15:20,199
That's exactly what I got.

375
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:21,079
No need to worry.

376
00:15:21,959 --> 00:15:22,600
Really?

377
00:15:26,600 --> 00:15:27,799
