386
00:15:52,160 --> 00:15:53,480
Let me recharge.

387
00:15:59,799 --> 00:16:00,760
To be honest,

388
00:16:01,799 --> 00:16:03,039
the shipyard case

389
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:04,880
and

390
00:16:05,520 --> 00:16:07,199
Tang Yuhui getting promoted to

391
00:16:07,719 --> 00:16:09,559
