393
00:16:13,679 --> 00:16:15,280
I might need some time

394
00:16:17,400 --> 00:16:19,000
to process all these.

395
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,319
I don't even know why

396
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:23,039
these things

397
00:16:24,079 --> 00:16:25,039
made me feel

398
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:26,719
so lacking in confidence right now.

399
00:16:27,520 --> 00:16:29,240
