407
00:17:01,679 --> 00:17:02,559
I just want to help you.

408
00:17:03,799 --> 00:17:04,880
But I just

409
00:17:05,160 --> 00:17:06,520
don't know how.

410
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:08,919
I'd love to support you

411
00:17:08,919 --> 00:17:09,799
in regaining

412
00:17:09,799 --> 00:17:11,079
your confidence,

413
00:17:11,880 --> 00:17:12,919
