414
00:17:16,959 --> 00:17:17,880
I understand.

415
00:17:21,439 --> 00:17:22,000
It's dad.

416
00:17:22,520 --> 00:17:22,799
OK,

417
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:23,719
I'll pack the stuff.

418
00:17:25,519 --> 00:17:26,040
Hello, dad.

419
00:17:34,560 --> 00:17:35,560
Dad, mom!

420
00:17:35,840 --> 00:17:36,560
You're here.

421
00:17:37,519 --> 00:17:38,400
What happened?

422
00:17:39,320 --> 00:17:40,439
They're operating on her now.

423
00:17:40,840 --> 00:17:42,400
Last night, she went to bed

424
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:43,880
earlier than usual.

425
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:45,320
We thought

426
00:17:45,600 --> 00:17:47,120
