427
00:17:47,120 --> 00:17:48,600
to wait for you to pick her up.

428
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:49,959
You planned to go to the cemetery, right?

429
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,479
So we didn't think much of it.

430
00:17:51,999 --> 00:17:53,479
But when we got up this morning,

431
00:17:53,479 --> 00:17:54,080
not long after,

432
00:17:54,199 --> 00:17:55,080
she fainted.

433
00:17:55,759 --> 00:17:56,919
It was my fault.

434
00:17:57,519 --> 00:17:57,880
I should have

435
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:59,040
been more attentive.

436
00:17:59,360 --> 00:17:59,759
Mom,

437
00:17:59,759 --> 00:18:00,360
don't say that.

438
00:18:00,719 --> 00:18:01,880
You got her here in time.

439
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:09,519
Doctor,

440
00:18:09,719 --> 00:18:10,640
