441
00:18:10,999 --> 00:18:11,719
Come to my office.

442
00:18:12,040 --> 00:18:12,840
I'll explain everything to you.

443
00:18:13,560 --> 00:18:13,999
Let's go.

444
00:18:13,999 --> 00:18:14,239
OK.

445
00:18:15,360 --> 00:18:15,919
I'm going.

446
00:18:21,560 --> 00:18:22,719
Your mother's cancer cells

447
00:18:22,999 --> 00:18:23,919
have spread significantly.

448
00:18:24,800 --> 00:18:26,120
Based on the current symptoms,

449
00:18:26,600 --> 00:18:27,999
they have started to spread to the brain.

450
00:18:28,719 --> 00:18:29,800
The exact extent of the spread

451
00:18:30,439 --> 00:18:31,199
will be determined after the test results

452
00:18:31,199 --> 00:18:31,840
are available.

453
00:18:32,840 --> 00:18:33,999
You have to prepare for the worst.

454
00:18:34,560 --> 00:18:35,600
The patient isn't likely

455
00:18:36,759 --> 00:18:37,560
to last much longer.

456
00:18:48,439 --> 00:18:48,880
Doctor.

457
00:18:50,439 --> 00:18:51,759
Not much longer?

458
00:18:53,519 --> 00:18:54,800
How long does she have left?

459
00:18:55,519 --> 00:18:56,199
Optimistically,

460
00:18:57,519 --> 00:18:58,239
