461
00:19:02,800 --> 00:19:03,519
One to two months?

462
00:19:07,919 --> 00:19:08,400
Then,

463
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:09,519
can we switch

464
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:11,679
to other chemotherapy medications?

465
00:19:12,919 --> 00:19:14,080
Starting radiation and chemotherapy now

466
00:19:14,679 --> 00:19:15,600
won't do much good.

467
00:19:15,679 --> 00:19:16,199
Moreover,

468
00:19:16,679 --> 00:19:17,360
her condition

469
00:19:17,600 --> 00:19:18,400
is not good enough for those.

470
00:19:25,759 --> 00:19:26,120
Doctor Zhao,

471
00:19:29,679 --> 00:19:30,199
please,

472
00:19:31,800 --> 00:19:32,519
please figure

473
00:19:32,519 --> 00:19:33,360
something out.

474
00:19:34,080 --> 00:19:35,160
No matter how much it costs,

475
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:36,320
no matter what it takes,

476
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:38,239
I will cooperate fully.

477
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:41,199
We will do our utmost.

478
00:20:01,040 --> 00:20:01,439
Xiaoning,

479
00:20:01,919 --> 00:20:02,439
take these.

480
00:20:03,279 --> 00:20:04,840
These are some meds mom often takes.

481
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:05,919
Tomorrow, when you're at the hospital,

482
00:20:05,919 --> 00:20:06,600
