490
00:20:22,999 --> 00:20:23,959
Zhouyang?

491
00:20:24,239 --> 00:20:25,919
Wasn't that case assigned to section two?

492
00:20:26,919 --> 00:20:27,279
Yes.

493
00:20:28,320 --> 00:20:29,800
But they couldn't finalize the deal.

494
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:31,239
I happen to have some connections.

495
00:20:40,999 --> 00:20:42,120
You're aiming to secure Zhouyang.

496
00:20:42,120 --> 00:20:43,279
It won't be easy, though.

497
00:20:43,679 --> 00:20:44,279
At the moment,

498
00:20:44,479 --> 00:20:46,239
many banks are vying for it.

499
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,400
If you get involved with it,

500
00:20:48,759 --> 00:20:49,800
you'll likely be

501
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:50,679
tied up for a long time.

502
00:20:51,560 --> 00:20:53,999
Mom will be transferred out of ICU tomorrow.

503
00:20:54,519 --> 00:20:56,719
The one she wants to see the most is you.

504
00:20:58,479 --> 00:21:00,080
In my view,

505
00:21:00,919 --> 00:21:02,519
you'd better spend more time with her.

506
00:21:06,679 --> 00:21:07,759
I went to the hospital today.

507
00:21:08,999 --> 00:21:09,800
The doctor told me that

508
00:21:10,160 --> 00:21:11,320
there was a special medicine abroad.

509
00:21:11,679 --> 00:21:12,320
Maybe it's effective for her.

510
00:21:14,279 --> 00:21:15,160
