535
00:25:01,959 --> 00:25:02,400
Come in.

536
00:25:04,360 --> 00:25:04,800
Director Ji,

537
00:25:06,679 --> 00:25:07,439
Hello, Xiaoning.

538
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:09,479
